b.17263-formula533"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-1250402x50_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>对<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-1250402x51_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，由<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-1250402x52_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，有</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.17263-formula534"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-1250402x53_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>所以当(1)式或(2)式成立时，均有</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.17263-formula535"><label>(6)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-1250402x54_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>由Holder不等式，得</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.17263-formula536"><label>(7)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-1250402x56_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>由<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-1250402x57_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>不等式 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.17263-ref4">4</xref>] 知</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.17263-formula537"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-1250402x58_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>对<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-1250402x59_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，有</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.17263-formula538"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-1250402x60_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>对<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-1250402x61_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，有</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.17263-formula539"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/6-1250402x62_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>所以当(1)式或(2)式成立时，均有